    "Full details of the current, most recent releases can be found here: https:// platf orm. openai.",
    "com/ docs/ models.",
    "In this study, we use GPT-3.5 models available publicly at the time of data collection, namely, gpt-3.5-turbo-0301 (the basis of ChatGPT at the time) and text-davinci-003.",
    "To use any of OpenAI's LLMs, the user must provide what is called a \"prompt\" from which the model will generate natural language.",
    "An example of such a prompt could be \"Please identify five plants native to New Mexico.\""
